 Omuro, Antonio M. and Pollack, Ian F. and Prados, Michael and Robins, H. Ian and Soffietti, Riccardo and Wu, Jing and Metellus, Phillipe and Tabori, Uri and Bartels, Ute and Bouffet, Eric and Hawkins, Cynthia E. and Rutka, James T. and Dirks, Peter and Pfister, Stefan M. and Merchant, Thomas E. and Gilbert, Mark R. and Armstrong, Terri S. and Korshunov, Andrey and Ellison, David W. and Taylor, Michael D.},
title = {Therapeutic Impact of Cytoreductive Surgery and Irradiation of Posterior Fossa Ependymoma in the Molecular Era: A Retrospective Multicohort Analysis},
